      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly softened, add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for a further 4-5 min or until the tomatoes have softened</p><p>Once softened, add your <strong>orzo</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains</p>",
      "order": 5,
