    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> stock </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo occasionally to stop it from sticking</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
