    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy tomato orzo</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>cheesy asparagus</strong> to the side (crispy side up)</p><p>Top with the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave the pine nuts and black pepper!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
